"If you don't want to speak to an operator, you don't need to enter any personal details and we don't store\n"
"    any of the information you have entered."
msgstr "Os nad ydych chi am siarad â gweithredwr, ni fydd angen i chi roi unrhyw fanylion personol a ni fyddwn ni’n storio unrhyw wybodaeth yr ydych chi wedi’i rhoi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:56
msgid ""
"To provide you with the best service that we can, Civil Legal Advice may share some information about you\n"
"    with other organisations. But we will only do this if you have given us permission."
msgstr "Er mwyn darparu’r gwasanaeth gorau posibl i chi, mae’n bosibl y bydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn rhannu rhywfaint o wybodaeth amdanoch chi â sefydliadau eraill. Ond dim ond os ydych chi wedi rhoi caniatâd i ni y byddwn ni’n gwneud hyn. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:61
msgid ""
"In exceptional circumstances, we may share limited information about you without your consent. This would\n"
"    only be to prevent fraud, help detect crime, if it is required by law or by a court order or If we are\n"
"    very worried about your safety or the safety of others."
msgstr "Mewn amgylchiadau eithriadol, gallwn ni rannu gwybodaeth benodol amdanoch heb gael eich caniatâd. Yr unig reswm y bydden ni’n gwneud hyn yw er mwyn atal twyll, helpu i ddarganfod troseddu, os yw’n ofynnol o dan y gyfraith neu orchymyn llys neu os ydyn ni’n pryderu’n fawr am eich diogelwch chi neu bobl eraill. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:67
msgid "Read the full Civil Legal Advice Privacy Statement here."
msgstr "Darllenwch Ddatganiad Preifatrwydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn llawn yma. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:71
msgid "Civil Legal Advice Privacy Statement"
msgstr "Datganiad Preifatrwydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:73
msgid ""
"In order to provide a service to you, Civil Legal Advice (<abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr>)\n"
"    may need to view, collect, record and hold (‘process’) personal data about you."
msgstr "Er mwyn darparu gwasanaeth i chi, mae’n bosibl y bydd angen i Gyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil (CLA) weld, casglu, cofnodi a dal (‘prosesu’) data personol amdanoch chi."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:77
msgid ""
"Personal data is information about you that can be used to identify you in some way\n"
"    e.g. your name or telephone number. You can look at the\n"
"    <a href=\"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions#personal-data\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">full legal definition</a>."
msgstr "Data personol yw gwybodaeth amdanoch chi y gellir ei defnyddio i’ch adnabod mewn rhyw ffordd e.e. eich enw neu rif ffôn. Gallwch weld y diffiniad cyfreithiol llawn yma: http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions#personal-data."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:82
msgid ""
"<abbr title=\"Civil Legal Advice\">CLA</abbr> is committed to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy.\n"
"    We are legally bound by the Data Protection Act 1998 to ensure that we only use your personal\n"
"    data for the reasons we tell you about. We must also hold it securely."
msgstr "Mae CLA wedi ymrwymo i ddiogelu’ch data personol a pharchu’ch preifatrwydd. Rydym wedi cael ein rhwymo’n gyfreithiol gan Ddeddf Diogelu Data 1998 i sicrhau mai dim ond am y rhesymau y byddwn yn eu rhoi i chi y byddwn yn defnyddio’ch data personol. Hefyd rhaid i ni eu dal yn ddiogel. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:87
msgid ""
"This statement explains how <abbr>CLA</abbr> will process any personal data that we collect\n"
"    from you or that you provide to us."
msgstr "Mae’r datganiad hwn yn egluro sut y bydd CLA yn prosesu unrhyw ddata personol y byddwn yn eu casglu oddi wrthych neu y byddwch yn eu darparu i ni."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:92
msgid "What is Civil Legal Advice?"
msgstr "Beth yw Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:94
msgid "is a national adviceline for England and Wales, paid for by Legal Aid."
msgstr "Mae Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil (CLA) yn llinell gyngor cenedlaethol ar gyfer Cymru a Lloegr sy’n cael ei hariannu drwy Gymorth Cyfreithiol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:97
msgid ""
"The Legal Aid Agency (<abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr>) is responsible for the <abbr>CLA</abbr>\n"
"    service and the Ministry of Justice (<abbr title=\"The Ministry of Justice\">MoJ</abbr>) is the Data Controller\n"
"    for the purposes of the Data Protection Act 1998. They are responsible for determining the purposes for which\n"
"    and the manner in which any personal data are, or are to be processed."
msgstr "Yr Asiantaeth Cymorth Cyfreithiol (LAA) sy’n gyfrifol am wasanaeth CLA a’r Weinyddiaeth Cyfiawnder yw’r Rheolydd Data i ddibenion Deddf Diogelu Data 1998. Maent yn gyfrifol am bennu’r dibenion y mae neu y bydd unrhyw ddata personol yn cael eu prosesu ar eu cyfer a’r ffordd o wneud hynny."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:103
msgid ""
"For a more comprehensive explanation see\n"
"    <a href=\"http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions#personal-data\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">this guide</a>."
msgstr "Mae esboniad mwy cynhwysfawr ar gael drwy ddilyn y ddolen isod: http://ico.org.uk/for_organisations/data_protection/the_guide/key_definitions#personal-data."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:107
msgid ""
"The <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr> works with other organisations who deliver the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service.\n"
"    For example when you first make contact with <abbr>CLA</abbr> you will communicate with\n"
"    the <abbr>CLA</abbr> Operator Service, which is delivered by Agilisys\n"
"    (a contractor employed by the <abbr title=\"The Legal Aid Agency\">LAA</abbr> to [  ])."
msgstr "Mae’r LAA yn cydweithio â sefydliadau eraill sy’n darparu gwasanaeth CLA. Er enghraifft, pan fyddwch yn cysylltu gyntaf â CLA, byddwch yn cyfathrebu â Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA, sy’n cael ei ddarparu gan Agilisys ar ran Freedom Communications (contractwr sy’n cael ei gyflogi gan yr LAA i ddarparu Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA). "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:113
msgid ""
"If after contacting the <abbr>CLA</abbr> Operator Service it is determined that you\n"
"    qualify for the <abbr>CLA</abbr> specialist advice service you may be put through\n"
"    to one of a number of <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialist Advice Providers. If you do not qualify to receive\n"
"    <abbr>CLA</abbr> specialist advice we will inform you accordingly and\n"
"    direct you to alternative help."
msgstr "Os penderfynir, wedi i chi gysylltu â Gwasanaeth Gweithredwyr CLA, eich bod yn gymwys i dderbyn gwasanaeth cynghori arbenigol CLA, gallech gael eich trosglwyddo i un o nifer o Ddarparwyr Cyngor Arbenigol CLA.  Os nad ydych yn gymwys i gael cyngor arbenigol CLA, byddwn yn rhoi gwybod i chi am hynny ac yn eich cyfeirio at leoedd eraill sy’n cynnig help."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:120
msgid ""
"These organisations are Data Processors for the purposes of the Data Protection Act 1998 which\n"
"    means that they process data on behalf of the <abbr>LAA</abbr> and <abbr title=\"The Ministry of Justice\">MoJ</abbr>."
msgstr "Mae’r sefydliadau hyn yn Broseswyr Data i ddibenion Deddf Diogelu Data 1998. Mae hyn yn golygu eu bod yn prosesu data ar ran yr LAA a’r Weinyddiaeth Cyfiawnder. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:124
msgid ""
"The <abbr>CLA</abbr> service is committed to following this Privacy Statement.\n"
"    <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialists must also adhere to their own internal privacy policy."
msgstr "Mae gwasanaeth CLA wedi ymrwymo i gydymffurfio â’r Datganiad Preifatrwydd hwn. Hefyd rhaid i Arbenigwyr CLA gydymffurfio â’u polisi preifatrwydd mewnol eu hunain."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:129
msgid "What data will <abbr>CLA</abbr> collect?"
msgstr "Pa ddata y bydd CLA yn eu casglu?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:131
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will only collect the minimum amount of information necessary in order\n"
"    to deliver the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service to you."
msgstr "Dim ond y wybodaeth sydd ei hangen i ddarparu gwasanaeth CLA i chi y bydd CLA yn ei chasglu."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:135
msgid "The kind of information <abbr>CLA</abbr> may collect about you includes:"
msgstr "Y math o wybodaeth y gall CLA ei chasglu amdanoch chi yw:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:139
msgid ""
"Personal details including your name, address, date of birth, contact details, diversity\n"
"      monitoring information and national insurance number;"
msgstr "Manylion personol gan gynnwys eich enw, cyfeiriad, dyddiad geni, manylion cysylltu, gwybodaeth ar gyfer monitro amrywiaeth a’ch rhif yswiriant gwladol;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:143
msgid "Financial information needed to determine if you qualify for legal aid;"
msgstr "Gwybodaeth ariannol sydd ei hangen i bennu a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:146
msgid "Reason for contacting <abbr>CLA</abbr>, such as the nature of your problem or specific details about your situation;"
msgstr "Y rheswm dros gysylltu â CLA, er enghraifft, natur eich problem neu fanylion penodol am eich sefyllfa;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:149
msgid "Details of any specific needs that you may have in order to access the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service;"
msgstr "Manylion am unrhyw anghenion penodol sydd gennych er mwyn defnyddio gwasanaeth CLA;"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:152
msgid ""
"Responses to any customer satisfaction survey or details of any feedback, complaints or requests\n"
"      for a review of our decision about whether you qualify for legal aid."
msgstr "Ymatebion i unrhyw arolwg o fodlonrwydd cwsmeriaid neu fanylion am unrhyw adborth, cwynion neu geisiadau am adolygu ein penderfyniad ynghylch a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:157
msgid ""
"The amount of information <abbr>CLA</abbr> will collect will depend on whether you qualify for the <abbr>CLA</abbr>\n"
"    service and/or your specific needs. For example you will be asked to provide more information\n"
"    before we can transfer you through to a <abbr>CLA</abbr> Specialist."
msgstr "Bydd maint y wybodaeth y mae CLA yn ei chasglu’n dibynnu ar ba un a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael gwasanaeth CLA neu beidio a/neu eich anghenion penodol. Er enghraifft, byddwn ni’n gofyn i chi ddarparu rhagor o wybodaeth cyn eich trosglwyddo i un o Arbenigwyr CLA."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:163
msgid "What does <abbr>CLA</abbr> use the data for?"
msgstr "Ar gyfer beth y mae CLA yn defnyddio’r data?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:164
msgid "collects and records information about you to:"
msgstr "Mae CLA yn casglu ac yn cofnodi gwybodaeth amdanoch chi er mwyn:"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:166
msgid "Work out whether you qualify for legal aid"
msgstr "Gweithio allan a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:167
msgid "Provide information and/or advice services to you"
msgstr "Darparu gwasanaethau gwybodaeth a/neu gyngor i chi"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:168
msgid "Save you from repeating information every time you contact us"
msgstr "Eich arbed rhag ailadrodd gwybodaeth bob tro y byddwch chi’n cysylltu â ni"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:169
msgid "Help us monitor and improve our service"
msgstr "Ein helpu i fonitro a gwella ein gwasanaeth "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:171
msgid ""
"Build statistics about the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service, monitor fraud and justify public expenditure.\n"
"      This information is collated in an anonymous format."
msgstr "Cael ystadegau am wasanaeth CLA, monitro twyll a chyfiawnhau gwariant cyhoeddus. Mae’r wybodaeth hon yn cael ei chasglu heb gynnwys enwau. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:175
msgid ""
"Collect views on the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service and any improvements considered necessary.\n"
"      Where consent is provided <abbr>CLA</abbr> User contact details may be passed onto an independent research agency."
msgstr "Casglu barn am wasanaeth CLA ac unrhyw welliannau sydd eu hangen. Os bydd defnyddwyr gwasanaeth CLA yn cydsynio, gellir trosglwyddo eu manylion cysylltu i asiantaeth ymchwil annibynnol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:178
msgid "Prevent or detect crime or fraud"
msgstr "Atal neu ddarganfod troseddu neu dwyll"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:181
msgid ""
"Given the purposes for which your personal data may be used (as referred to above)\n"
"    it is essential that the information you provide is accurate and complete."
msgstr "Oherwydd y dibenion y gellir defnyddio eich data personol ar eu cyfer (sydd wedi’u nodi uchod), mae’n hanfodol eich bod yn darparu gwybodaeth sy’n gywir a chyflawn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:186
msgid "How does <abbr>CLA</abbr> collect your personal data and keep it safe?"
msgstr "Sut y mae CLA yn casglu’ch data personol ac yn eu cadw’n ddiogel?"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:188
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> may collect personal data about you by phone, online, email or post (see table below).\n"
"    Any personal data will be recorded and stored within a secure system that meets required Government standards."
msgstr "Gall CLA gasglu data personol amdanoch chi dros y ffôn, ar-lein, drwy’r post a’r e-bost (gweler y tabl isod). Bydd unrhyw ddata personol yn cael eu cofnodi a’u storio mewn system ddiogel sy’n cyrraedd safonau sydd wedi’u gosod gan y Llywodraeth."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:192
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will be able to view and verify the information that you provide and where\n"
"    necessary will amend it to maintain its accuracy."
msgstr "Bydd CLA yn gallu gweld a dilysu’r wybodaeth yr ydych chi’n ei darparu ac, os bydd angen, bydd yn ei newid er mwyn ei chadw’n gywir."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:196
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of personal data that <abbr>CLA</abbr> will ask to collect is your name and one other piece\n"
"    of personal information that could be used to identify you e.g. postcode, date of birth or telephone number."
msgstr "Y data personol lleiaf y bydd CLA yn gofyn am eu casglu yw’ch enw ac un eitem arall o wybodaeth bersonol i’w defnyddio i’ch adnabod os bydd angen e.e. cod post, dyddiad geni neu rif ffôn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:200
msgid ""
"All personal data will be stored on secure servers in the UK. It may also be stored outside of Europe,\n"
"    where it could be viewed by our staff or specialist providers."
msgstr "Bydd yr holl ddata personol yn cael eu storio ar weinyddion diogel yn y DU. Gellir eu storio y tu allan i Ewrop hefyd, lle y bydd ein staff neu ddarparwyr arbenigol yn gallu eu gweld. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:204
msgid ""
"By submitting your personal data, you agree to information being recorded, used and stored\n"
"    as outlined in this Privacy Statement."
msgstr "Drwy gyflwyno’ch data personol, rydych chi’n cytuno i’r wybodaeth gael ei chofnodi, ei defnyddio a’i storio’n unol â’r Datganiad Preifatrwydd hwn."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:208
msgid "How we collect and store your personal data"
msgstr "Sut yr ydym yn casglu ac yn storio’ch data personol"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:211
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Ffôn"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:213
msgid ""
"When you call <abbr>CLA</abbr> we will record relevant personal data that you provide within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        We may also record your calls. But you can choose to opt out of this or choose whether or not\n"
"        to continue with the call.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        If you leave <abbr>CLA</abbr> a voice message we will record the minimum amount of information\n"
"        required in order to contact you back."
msgstr "Pan fyddwch chi’n ffonio CLA, byddwn ni’n cofnodi data personol perthnasol yr ydych chi’n eu rhoi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Gallwn recordio’ch galwadau hefyd. Ond cewch chi ddewis peidio ag ymuno â hyn neu ddewis a ydych chi am barhau â’r alwad neu beidio. Os byddwch chi’n gadael neges llais i CLA, byddwn ni’n cofnodi’r lleiaf o wybodaeth sydd ei hangen i gysylltu â chi wedyn. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:223
msgid "Online"
msgstr "Ar-lein"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:225
msgid ""
"When you contact <abbr>CLA</abbr> online the personal data that you provide will be recorded within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        Please note that transmitting information over the internet is generally not completely secure, and\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> can’t guarantee the security of your data. Any data you transmit is at your own risk.\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> have procedures and security features in place to keep your data secure once we receive it."
msgstr "Pan fyddwch chi’n cysylltu â CLA ar-lein, bydd y data personol yr ydych chi’n eu darparu’n cael eu cofnodi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Cofiwch nad yw gwybodaeth sy’n cael ei throsglwyddo dros y rhyngrwyd yn hollol ddiogel yn gyffredinol, ac nid yw CLA yn gallu gwarantu y bydd eich data’n ddiogel. Ar eich menter eich hun y byddwch chi’n trosglwyddo unrhyw ddata. Mae CLA wedi rhoi gweithdrefnau a chyfleusterau diogelwch ar waith i gadw’ch data’n ddiogel wedi i ni eu cael."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:235
msgid ""
"Transmitting information via email is generally not completely secure, and <abbr>CLA</abbr> can’t guarantee the\n"
"        security of your data. Any data you transmit is at your own risk.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> have procedures and security features in place to keep your data secure once we receive it.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        When you email <abbr>CLA</abbr>, relevant personal data that you provide will be recorded within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> may monitor and store both your incoming and outgoing emails. We may also use blocking software,"
msgstr "Nid yw gwybodaeth sy’n cael ei throsglwyddo drwy’r e-bost yn hollol ddiogel yn gyffredinol, ac nid yw CLA yn gallu gwarantu y bydd eich data’n ddiogel. Ar eich menter eich hun y byddwch chi’n trosglwyddo unrhyw ddata. Mae CLA wedi rhoi gweithdrefnau a chyfleusterau diogelwch ar waith i gadw’ch data’n ddiogel wedi i ni eu cael. Pan fyddwch chi’n anfon neges e-bost i CLA, bydd data personol perthnasol yr ydych chi’n eu darparu yn cael eu cofnodi mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Mae CLA yn gallu monitro a storio negeseuon e-bost oddi wrthych chi ac atoch chi. Hefyd gallwn ddefnyddio meddalwedd rhwystro. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:246
msgid "Post"
msgstr "Post"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:248
msgid ""
"When <abbr>CLA</abbr> receives post we may record relevant personal data included within a secure digital system.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> may also retain original hard-copies of information submitted by you. This must be stored in a locked\n"
"        filing cabinet. Digital copies of letters may be scanned and stored."
msgstr "Pan fydd CLA yn derbyn llythyrau, gallwn ni gofnodi data personol perthnasol sydd ynddynt mewn system ddigidol ddiogel. Hefyd gall CLA gadw llythyrau gwreiddiol sy’n cynnwys gwybodaeth a gyflwynwyd gennych chi. Rhaid storio’r rhain mewn cwpwrdd ffeiliau sydd wedi’i gloi. Gellir sganio copïau digidol o lythyrau a’u storio. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:257
msgid "Keeping your personal data safe from others"
msgstr "Cadw’ch data personol yn ddiogel oddi wrth eraill"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:260
msgid "Repeat Contacts"
msgstr "Ailgysylltu"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:262
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will not disclose any personal information to anyone contacting the <abbr>CLA</abbr> service until\n"
"        they have successfully verified that their identity matches that of an existing record."
msgstr "Ni fydd CLA yn datgelu unrhyw wybodaeth bersonol i rywun sy’n cysylltu â gwasanaeth CLA nes ei fod wedi cadarnhau bod ei hunaniaeth yn cyfateb i gofnod sy’n bodoli. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:267
msgid "Third-parties"
msgstr "Trydydd parti"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:269
msgid ""
"<abbr>CLA</abbr> will accept contact made by a third-party on behalf of another person. The third party has to\n"
"        demonstrate they have appropriate authority to act on your behalf.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        <abbr>CLA</abbr> must record the relationship between the third-party and the individual seeking advice\n"
"        and whether they are authorised to act on their behalf.\n"
"        <br><br>\n"
"        They must also agree a password to verify the identity of the third-party if they contact the service again."
msgstr "Bydd CLA yn cydnabod trydydd parti sy’n cysylltu ar ran person arall. Mae’n rhaid i’r trydydd parti ddangos bod ganddynt yr awdurdod priodol i weithredu ar eich rhan. Rhaid i CLA gofnodi’r berthynas rhwng y trydydd parti a’r unigolyn sy’n gofyn am gyngor ac a yw’r trydydd parti wedi’i awdurdodi i weithredu ar ei ran. Hefyd rhaid i CLA gytuno ar gyfrinair er mwyn gwirio hunaniaeth y trydydd parti os bydd yn cysylltu â’r gwasanaeth eto."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:279
msgid "Outgoing Communications"
msgstr "Anfon negeseuon allan"

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:281
msgid "<abbr>CLA</abbr> may need to contact you directly."
msgstr "Mae’n bosibl y bydd angen i CLA gysylltu â chi’n uniongyrchol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:283
msgid "In order to protect privacy <abbr>CLA</abbr> will always check with you what forms of outgoing communication are acceptable and appropriate and whether messages can be left."
msgstr "Er mwyn diogelu preifatrwydd, bydd CLA bob amser yn gofyn pa ddulliau o gyfathrebu â chi sy’n dderbyniol a phriodol ac a allwn ni adael negeseuon. "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:285
msgid "When making outgoing calls to you <abbr>CLA</abbr> will ensure that:"
msgstr "Pan fydd CLA yn eich ffonio, bydd yn sicrhau: "

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:288
msgid ""
"Call backs are only made where you have agreed to this. Authorised third parties\n"
"            acting on your behalf can give agreement."
msgstr "Mai dim ond os ydych chi wedi cytuno ar hynny y byddwn ni’n ffonio’n ôl. Gall trydydd parti gytuno ar hyn os yw wedi’i awdurdodi i weithredu ar eich rhan."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:292
msgid ""
"Where a call back is made to you and there is no answer and a message taker is available,\n"
"            no message will be left unless you have previously given specific instructions that this would be acceptable."
msgstr "Os yw’n ffonio’n ôl ac nad oes ateb, a bod recordydd negeseuon ar gael, na fydd yn gadael neges oni bai eich bod wedi rhoi cyfarwyddiadau penodol cyn hynny fod hyn yn dderbyniol."

#: cla_public/templates/privacy.html:296
msgid ""
"Where the phone is answered and someone other than you answers the phone and says that you are\n"
