#: cla_public/templates/result/confirmation.html:52
msgid ""
"If the operator you speak to thinks you might qualify, they will\n"
"    put you through to a CLA specialist adviser. Your CLA specialist adviser will\n"
"    ask you more questions before making the final decision about whether you\n"
"    qualify for legal aid."
msgstr "Os bydd y gweithredwr rydych yn siarad ag o'n credu y gallwch fod yn gymwys, cewch eich trosglwyddo i siarad â chynghorydd arbenigol y CLA. Bydd eich cynghorydd arbenigol CLA yn gofyn rhagor o gwestiynau i chi cyn gwneud y penderfyniad terfynol pa un a ydych yn gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol ai peidio."

#: cla_public/templates/result/confirmation.html:59
msgid ""
"You will need to provide evidence of your financial circumstances\n"
"    and maybe your problem. Your CLA specialist adviser will explain\n"
"    what is needed."
