#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible-no-callback.html:10
msgid ""
"Civil Legal Advice does not provide advice about issues\n"
"      related to welfare benefits but you may be able to get free advice from\n"
"      a legal adviser in your area. "
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible-no-callback.html:16
msgid ""
"To get advice about appealing a decision made by the social\n"
"      security tribunal about your benefits to the Upper Tribunal, Court of\n"
"      Appeal or Supreme Court, you should contact a legal adviser.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible-no-callback.html:23
#: cla_public/templates/result/face-to-face.html:56
msgid ""
"Your adviser will check whether you qualify for legal aid at\n"
"    no cost to you. If you qualify for legal aid, you will not have to pay\n"
"      for legal advice."
msgstr "Bydd y cynghorydd cyfreithiol yn gweld a ydych chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol. Ni ddylech chi orfod talu am y gwiriad hwn. "

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible-no-callback.html:29
#: cla_public/templates/result/face-to-face.html:62
msgid ""
"If you don't qualify for legal aid, you will have to pay for\n"
"      legal advice. You should ask your adviser about the cost of their\n"
"      advice."
msgstr "Os na fyddwch chi’n gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol, dylech chi siarad â’ch cynghorydd am y gost o gael cyngor"

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:6
msgid "We need more information"
msgstr "Mae angen i ni gael rhagor o wybodaeth"

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:14
msgid ""
"In order to decide whether you might qualify for legal aid, we need more information about\n"
"      your financial circumstances. You should contact Civil Legal Advice."
msgstr "Er mwyn penderfynu a allech chi fod yn gymwys i gael cymorth cyfreithiol, mae angen i ni gael rhagor o wybodaeth am eich amgylchiadau ariannol. "

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:18
msgid ""
"The first person you speak to will be a CLA operator. They will check what\n"
"      you told us already. They will also ask you some more questions about your financial\n"
"      circumstances and to find out if your specific problem is covered by legal aid."
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:24
msgid ""
"Based on the answers you’ve given today, you might qualify financially for legal aid.\n"
"      Contact Civil Legal Advice (CLA), a national helpline for England and Wales, to find out for certain\n"
"      if you qualify, and get specialist advice if you do."
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:30
msgid ""
"Please submit your details to get your personal case reference number.\n"
"    You will need to quote this number when you speak with CLA."
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:34
msgid ""
"You can choose to contact CLA yourself and speak to someone immediately (this is an 0345 number -\n"
"    <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/call-charges\" rel=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">call charges</a> apply)\n"
"    or ask us to call you back, which is free."
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:52
msgid ""
"Your CLA specialist adviser will ask you more questions before making the final decision about\n"
"      whether you qualify for legal aid."
