#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:57
msgid ""
"You will need to provide evidence of your financial circumstances and maybe your problem.\n"
"      Your CLA specialist adviser will explain what is needed."
msgstr "Bydd angen i chi ddarparu tystiolaeth o’ch amgylchiadau ariannol ac efallai eich problem. Bydd y cynghorydd arbenigol CLA yn egluro beth sydd ei angen."

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:62
msgid ""
"If your CLA specialist adviser takes your case on they will communicate with you by telephone,\n"
"      email or post."
msgstr "Os bydd y cynghorydd arbenigol CLA yn ymgymryd â’ch achos, bydd yn cyfathrebu â chi dros y ffôn neu drwy’r post neu e-bost."

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:67
msgid "If CLA can’t help we will always suggest other places that might be able to."
msgstr "Os nad yw CLA yn gallu helpu, byddwn ni bob amser yn awgrymu lleoedd eraill a allai’ch helpu."

#: cla_public/templates/result/eligible.html:71
msgid ""
"If your Civil Legal Advice adviser decides that you need to speak to someone in person or if\n"
"      you need someone to represent you in court, they will organise this for you."
msgstr "Os bydd y cynghorydd Cyngor Cyfreithiol Sifil yn penderfynu bod angen i chi siarad â rhywun eich hun neu os bydd arnoch chi angen rhywun i’ch cynrychioli yn y llys, fe fydd yn trefnu hyn i chi."

#: cla_public/templates/result/face-to-face.html:8
msgid "You might be able to get legal aid if your problem is about discrimination"
msgstr ""

#: cla_public/templates/result/face-to-face.html:11
msgid ""
"If you feel you’ve been discriminated against at work, we\n"
"        might be able to help. Please go back to the <a href=\"/\">start</a> and choose\n"
"        ‘Discrimination’ from the list of problem areas."
msgstr ""

